{"tid":375542,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"奧地利 + 捷克 旅行求教","createTime":"2017-08-26T14:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T01:02:55.000Z","uid":29260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a07de4ce9e7655a1fc800c822a9f6298479b4db","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？"},{"pid":"b5ca12b7dc75d53c0aa58fb71229074593617e37","tid":375542,"uid":138999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩係去過austria<br />\n巴士同火車都ok，但我試過巴士唔準時, 然後連帶我其他行程都delay埋 除左依樣都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n火車飛我記得可以上網訂再係火車站d機入code print番出黎<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt可以係town行 可以坐船 可以去鹽礦 同埋可以買包餵鴨餵天鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012ba4a422e4adbad8f39d98ff320f14398b55d0","tid":375542,"uid":68897,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"唔建議去hallstatt,個鎮好多人同好細，景麻麻地靚"},{"pid":"95558651ee082f0562812250e129f3d3c2e13dfe","tid":375542,"uid":560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩係去過austria<br />\n巴士同火車都ok，但我試過巴士唔準時, 然後連帶我其他行程都delay埋 除左依樣都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n火車飛我記得可以上網訂再係火車站d機入code print番出黎<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt可以係town行 可以坐船 可以去鹽礦 同埋可以買包餵鴨餵天鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我4月去 我就搭巴士轉火車 因為用既時間差不多 又平D<br />\nHallstatt景靚 個陣仲有雪落 勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢家去仲有five fingers可以去 4月未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鹽礦好值得去 <br />\nBTW, 你係2,3,4晚都係Hallstatt留夜?<br />\nPRAGUE 我個人覺得真係一日都夠 CK留一日好過PRAGUE留多日"},