天鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我最怕就係搵唔到巴士站/月台，miss 車就煩。"},{"pid":"aa7ea2ea2708b9616e54a8756939e0812bb670d4","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩係去過austria<br />\n巴士同火車都ok，但我試過巴士唔準時, 然後連帶我其他行程都delay埋 除左依樣都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n火車飛我記得可以上網訂再係火車站d機入code print番出黎<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt可以係town行 可以坐船 可以去鹽礦 同埋可以買包餵鴨餵天鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我4月去 我就搭巴士轉火車 因為用既時間差不多 又平D<br />\nHallstatt景靚 個陣仲有雪落 勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢家去仲有five fingers可以去 4月未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鹽礦好值得去 <br />\nBTW, 你係2,3,4晚都係Hallstatt留夜?<br />\nPRAGUE 我個人覺得真係一日都夠 CK留一日好過PRAGUE留多日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我改3-5 留Hallstatt ,1-3 Salzburg <br />\n有女性朋友同行，留時間俾佢地係Prague 掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec84437f4f53ecbd856f6f6a01926189cbfda20e","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩日幾係Hallstatt有d多既感覺，會唔會考慮撥一日比salzburg 去國王湖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會呀，睇完Ching 建議，上網睇哇真係值得去"},{"pid":"67d3acb691e04ebe4c59a2be9697785ffe552d2c","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"睇完咁多建議，感覺<br />\n<br />\n［更新］<br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 去國王湖<br />\n3/10 to Hallstatt (趕到就即日下午去鹽礦）<br />\n4/10 上 five fingers + ice cave <br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [睇到有bus 3hrs 直到］<br />\n6/10 下午去Prague <br />\n7/10 stay Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n酒店真係full full 地，中秋國X 連假去貴好多。（仲要2間兩人房） 而家都唔多選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n布搵格同ck 小鎮 洗唔洗提早book 車飛？ 我未睇到捷克既部份<br />\n<br />\n另，想再請教 你地係市內景點，通常都係行路去定買day pass ？"},{"pid":"2a01512201286c5935b2816fc6606e915e8e55b5","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上年去留左係Hallstatt 2日，去salt mine 同five figure 個座山<br />\n去Hallstatt 前一日就去左國王湖<br />\n2個地方都好值得去！<br />\n<br />\n國王湖:::<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/103359_535d16d4307387b63f72bfab94ad28a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F103359_535d16d4307387b63f72bfab94ad28a6.jpg&h=b11a23b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHallstatt::<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/103437_bbc6b2e1b06e5d686e2815aa7c536938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F103437_bbc6b2e1b06e5d686e2815aa7c536938.jpg&h=2f1f82d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/103448_1416343abf70cfc243b5305a09836293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F103448_1416343abf70cfc243b5305a09836293.jpg&h=4a610a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到five figure 座山先發現山上佈滿雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年10月去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/103635_0c9cfeff5d4780cbeaef685eba0a9d73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F103635_0c9cfeff5d4780cbeaef685eba0a9d73.jpg&h=eb551044&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/103637_9043f275a29abd6f95895d430519f186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F103637_9043f275a29abd6f95895d430519f186.jpg&h=088dc7aa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f14ae112ca87ccfa465517c57c93fcae1ea8901","tid":375542,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:54:25.000Z","msg":"我果時係prague &gt; ck &gt; hallstatt<br />\n全部一早book定<br />\n<br />\nprague to ck搭student agency，好舒服有野飲又有電視睇<br />\n<br />\nck to hallstatt搭 bean shuttle，酒店門前pickup，到hallstatt巴士站<br />\n<br />\n既然住宿都book好曬<br />\n咁不如車都book埋，都無乜野好改動"},{"pid":"ed86a59c9151c96a242d64ec6722b115c2e6c35f","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T20:31:18.000Z","msg":"我而家係電話 obb app 到訂飛，頂，入完credit card 資料，按完PAY, 就出 error , 試左好多次都係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好能驚 無哂平車飛，仲要唔知有無被扣錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/043114_0565f57e2d4613faf0c1b2b0bd566949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F043114_0565f57e2d4613faf0c1b2b0bd566949.jpg&h=fb0ee085&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/043114_b1da6115f5f874da1a80bfeaaaca04f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F043114_b1da6115f5f874da1a80bfeaaaca04f5.jpg&h=5b6787bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/043115_f8d7b1b0a1f755b9b3b78be63d173e19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F043115_f8d7b1b0a1f755b9b3b78be63d173e19.jpg&h=a2f6e703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5592ff8ffe5cda1195f457df076905feb1a97ac0","tid":375542,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T20:36:05.000Z","msg":"痴撚線,每個地方一晚(少於一日)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef32108ee0fd2d6f2b5ad1a1037fe171028f49d","tid":375542,"uid":129058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:20:40.000Z","msg":"個人覺得prague值得留多日行下<br />\n反而wien/ck可以縮短少少<br />\n有時間可以去埋st wolfgang搭架火車上山，真係好靚"},{"pid":"8675353e3b257ada6a9572421db00fb0a0f52084","tid":375542,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線,每個地方一晚(少於一日)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲人鍾意趕行程<br />\n始終香港人啲假少<br />\n<br />\n其實樓主唔怕趕都ok嘅 但可能去完唔覺去咗 <br />\n<br />\n樓主會唔會想一個地方留耐啲，cut少啲地方，因為有啲地方會無咁好玩。<br />\n<br />\n不過你係plan嚟每個地方打下卡咁就照咁plan啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b25d4764ea74c51fb687577d229767e6141b6b0","tid":375542,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:29:26.000Z","msg":"Hallstt 3日好似太多 但如果你鍾意呢個地方都可以嘅 <br />\n<br />\n因為個到其實好細"},{"pid":"607c9dd2cd178f5c5d9eaeeb643aff63e832de79","tid":375542,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:31:28.000Z","msg":"同埋Prague一晚唔夠 不過有啲人話Prague麻麻地 我自己覺得其實ok 都係睇你喜好"},{"pid":"2ac85393161477ef042475a51c36144d2d028966","tid":375542,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T22:09:16.000Z","msg":"行程chur到咁其實都幾辛苦，同埋會錯過好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHallstatt好靚，起碼半/一日小鎮一日上山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0u53o2le\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0u53o2le&h=c77ed1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8lmf4pid\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8lmf4pid&h=61547a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國王湖都幾值得去<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wu2s180o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwu2s180o&h=35de0188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人習慣每個(大)城市都起碼留幾日，起Prague 4日都唔覺得悶，當然難攞假係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ku2aohij\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fku2aohij&h=d215a647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t0x7ofkg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft0x7ofkg&h=fdddc3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVienna都一樣4日，好多人都話悶但我就好鐘意，靜靜地唔太多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8ov5e37p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8ov5e37p&h=2b69c25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過ck真係半日行得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wcd41tfp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwcd41tfp&h=facdb49a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"362452b89e2b4e9b07bd6997093a2e8b83e9ea28","tid":375542,"uid":53981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T22:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完咁多建議，感覺<br />\n<br />\n［更新］<br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 去國王湖<br />\n3/10 to Hallstatt (趕到就即日下午去鹽礦）<br />\n4/10 上 five fingers + ice cave <br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [睇到有bus 3hrs 直到］<br />\n6/10 下午去Prague <br />\n7/10 stay Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n酒店真係full full 地，中秋國X 連假去貴好多。（仲要2間兩人房） 而家都唔多選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n布搵格同ck 小鎮 洗唔洗提早book 車飛？ 我未睇到捷克既部份<br />\n<br />\n另，想再請教 你地係市內景點，通常都係行路去定買day pass ？</blockquote><br />\nPrague去ck我坐火車，沿途都幾靚而且冇乜人坐。我係個朝去到火車站先買飛嘅，return ticket好似5百幾kc, open ticket黎，坐幾點車翻都得，不過自己留意坐尾班車時間。<br />\n<br />\n市內就睇你住得近唔近市中心啦，你得個一日都去唔到啲遠嘅地方，行應該都冇問題。btw市內啲tram好似個個都係逃票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a6f0992733a66e554ff88d727dfa80e2219b0d","tid":375542,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T23:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線,每個地方一晚(少於一日)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲人鍾意趕行程<br />\n始終香港人啲假少<br />\n<br />\n其實樓主唔怕趕都ok嘅 但可能去完唔覺去咗 <br />\n<br />\n樓主會唔會想一個地方留耐啲，cut少啲地方，因為有啲地方會無咁好玩。<br />\n<br />\n不過你係plan嚟每個地方打下卡咁就照咁plan啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主趕到每個地方以小時計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0ba02f1002b7dbb0e723ded5ce0c0c04ab5467","tid":375542,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n恕我直言，你個行程好撚chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd3a1608a4e3ca9d4272acffe43ffccbf231247","tid":375542,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩晚Hallstatt 太多。。。可以去國王湖行下"},{"pid":"82f89bab383649c29f9c6ea6983545f6084ee9d8","tid":375542,"uid":36813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"prague 始終大過hallstatt 同ck <br />\n建議你留兩日<br />\n<br />\nhallstatt 同ck 小鎮黎<br />\n基本上1~1.5日就玩完一個地方<br />\n<br />\n我之前就<br />\nwien <br />\nSalzburg  <br />\n國王湖 <br />\nhallstatt <br />\nck<br />\nprague"},{"pid":"46a5485177ce19193bddabbc46aa24f0b56eeaf4","tid":375542,"uid":36813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"我自己由hallstatt 去ck ck 去prague 都是坐巴士<br />\n時間同火車差唔多<br />\n但好平<br />\n上網可以買定仲可以劃位<br />\n黃色既 你上網google 下<br />\n好多台灣人有教學<br />\n<br />\n至於austria 部份我坐火車"},{"pid":"5fe92b260884d1b007c0b7667a5ebd906d98345e","tid":375542,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"今年去過晒<br />\nHallstatt ck值得既<br />\nOBB 早三個月買就平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國一土<blockquote>湖值得去</blockquote>"},{"pid":"be909e255d501050d0f3ec948f7d418fc00b5ff7","tid":375542,"uid":36813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己由hallstatt 去ck <span style=\"color: red;\">就坐包車果d shuttle</span><br />\nck 去prague 就坐巴士<br />\n時間同火車差唔多<br />\n但好平<br />\n上網可以買定仲可以劃位<br />\n黃色既 你上網google 下<br />\n好多台灣人有教學<br />\n<br />\n至於austria 部份我坐火車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠"},{"pid":"3e3aebfa6c6d1ef0aae35b1db19c301493b4d553","tid":375542,"uid":8222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"Innsbruck 點樣可以去到新天鵝堡？<br />\n我睇巴士得來回各一班<br />\n坐半車就要返慕尼黑"},{"pid":"86ee6c14cc03eff627a5ce3e4e203143b8e99653","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:04:46.000Z","msg":"無計啦，港豬係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實一定要放棄某啲野<br />\n我再調整過行程<br />\n盡量每個城市到去到 啲值得睇既野<br />\n畢竟假難拎，去一轉就盡量去多幾個城市<br />\n<br />\nWien 留兩日，<br />\nInnsburg 一日行得哂<br />\nSalzburg 兩日行市內同去睇湖<br />\nHallstatt 事實都係兩日，<br />\n因為交通都食左時間<br />\n<br />\nCK 我應該都係一晚<br />\n兩日就Prague <br />\n剩返半日都坐飛機"},{"pid":"19577cbe397d229f0933e16c7a60c098de2565fa","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟同朋友一行4人<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n<br />\n28/9 當地時間 1300 到Wien <br />\n29/9 stay in Wien <br />\n30/9 to Innsbruck [0530 - 0944, 96歐]<br />\n1/10 to Salzburg [0914-1102, 56歐]<br />\n2/10 to Hallstatt [1412-1647, 41歐]<br />\n3-4/10 stay in Hallstatt<br />\n5/10 to CK 小鎮 [1107-1655, 76歐］<br />\n6/10 stay Cesky Krumlov<br />\n7/10 to Prague <br />\n8/10 1400 出發往機場返港<br />\n<br />\n我全程都係打算坐obb train ，<br />\n見佢早買飛有平，但見早前啲post 話巴輕平，請教下咁既火車價錢都Ok嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想confirm 係唔係 e-ticket ，定要到車站拎飛？睇官網唔太有講，淆淆地底。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 有咩正野？ 我見官網係話行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其他都唔知，求指點<br />\n<br />\n留一日係Prague 會唔會唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩晚Hallstatt 太多。。。可以去國王湖行下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt 去 sand mine &amp; five finger , 所以晚都差不多。因為我去到果日已經下午，只能鎮內行，第二日上山，而第三日下午去Cesky Krumlov 所以實際唔多"},{"pid":"6e93a74a9afa49196b81609d017bdc3898465703","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行程chur到咁其實都幾辛苦，同埋會錯過好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHallstatt好靚，起碼半/一日小鎮一日上山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0u53o2le\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0u53o2le&h=c77ed1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8lmf4pid\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8lmf4pid&h=61547a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國王湖都幾值得去<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wu2s180o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwu2s180o&h=35de0188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人習慣每個(大)城市都起碼留幾日，起Prague 4日都唔覺得悶，當然難攞假係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ku2aohij\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fku2aohij&h=d215a647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t0x7ofkg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft0x7ofkg&h=fdddc3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVienna都一樣4日，好多人都話悶但我就好鐘意，靜靜地唔太多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8ov5e37p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8ov5e37p&h=2b69c25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過ck真係半日行得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wcd41tfp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwcd41tfp&h=facdb49a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我有預到時間係Hallstatt 上山同行鎮，Salzburg 會去國王湖，<br />\n<br />\n去到Ck 都5點，所以留一晚第二日行一陣先去布拉格。<br />\n<br />\n我都想留耐啲，但 假無咁多，又兩日時間哂左係飛機到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b77094cd086cb87658cbac5cbd80184f88221b8","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己由hallstatt 去ck ck 去prague 都是坐巴士<br />\n時間同火車差唔多<br />\n但好平<br />\n上網可以買定仲可以劃位<br />\n黃色既 你上網google 下<br />\n好多台灣人有教學<br />\n<br />\n至於austria 部份我坐火車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係咁plan，但obb 我訂唔到，係咁error"},{"pid":"412f5f03a22788b64f0db55627093e00c44c0cb3","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Innsbruck 點樣可以去到新天鵝堡？<br />\n我睇巴士得來回各一班<br />\n坐半車就要返慕尼黑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係知有巴士到，但無研究"},{"pid":"68c3b4a96db2c6486be4181a290bf32f6cf6f231","tid":375542,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"話說我冬天去，五點就天黑，仲要每日 10點先出發，但同樓主預既日數差唔多，完全唔覺chur，仲幾hea下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9470b3e29e6902aa37dac1a3ed66c9eb11b7042","tid":375542,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"其實真係可以考慮shuttle 真心幾方便<br />\nDoor to door完全唔使擔心行李"},{"pid":"4cac1635cda9428bd6d8a80cb441bf3ffb36d6c1","tid":375542,"uid":8222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"Ck邊度可放行李<br />\n拎住件大行李想玩半日之後再上路"},{"pid":"dbc6b4a93a1bcbeb6d36e87801716289a80d3849","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ck邊度可放行李<br />\n拎住件大行李想玩半日之後再上路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見Hallstatt tourist information center 有寄存服務。唔知CEsky Krumlov 有無"},{"pid":"bc4822a754b83b9f7026231b924fa894d8580157","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真係可以考慮shuttle 真心幾方便<br />\nDoor to door完全唔使擔心行李</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會呀，揀ckshuttle<br />\n但我唔明non door to door 同 door to door ，我對車，無咩了解"},{"pid":"307181f6ffa6177483a1d527639796991b3596ca","tid":375542,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說我冬天去，五點就天黑，仲要每日 10點先出發，但同樓主預既日數差唔多，完全唔覺chur，仲幾hea下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你同我去既地點都一樣架？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得行程（地點to 地點）係密，但行起上來應該唔會chur , 因為我唔會深究啲皇宮，太花時間。<br />\n<br />\n（自己一個就會狂睇歷史野）"},{"pid":"184eb295b607bf01e7a34819d472f093fa396a61","tid":375542,"uid":78447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實真係可以考慮shuttle 真心幾方便<br />\nDoor to door完全唔使擔心行李</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會呀，揀ckshuttle<br />\n但我唔明non door to door 同 door to door ，我對車，無咩了解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDoor to door 係你指定嘅地點上車送去你指定嘅地點<br />\nNon door to door 係佢嘅地點上車同落車，通常係附近嘅旅行社或者一啲酒店大門口或者地標<br />\n<br />\n梗係揀door to door, 除非你啱啱好住係附近, 唔係就冇咗搭shuttle 嘅意義"},{"pid":"30f6e91ec6986e87c85a411fc0cae17e83968f86","tid":375542,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無計啦，港豬係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實一定要放棄某啲野<br />\n我再調整過行程<br />\n盡量每個城市到去到 啲值得睇既野<br />\n畢竟假難拎，去一轉就盡量去多幾個城市<br />\n<br />\nWien 留兩日，<br />\nInnsburg 一日行得哂<br />\nSalzburg 兩日行市內同去睇湖<br />\nHallstatt 事實都係兩日，<br />\n因為交通都食左時間<br />\n<br />\nCK 我應該都係一晚<br />\n兩日就Prague <br />\n剩返半日都坐飛機</blockquote><br />\n布拉格一日夠，真心"},{"pid":"215c2762519715dec94a18673bd3103b29db4f91","tid":375542,"uid":3980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:07:29.000Z","msg":"小弟宜家身在奧地利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身因為exchange要過嚟 家母同細佬跟埋嚟個幾禮拜 本身hea plan路線都冇plan行程 同埋酒店都係一個禮拜前bk 所以都好貴 三個人咁多晚都過萬二 因為我唔肯屈蛇 姐係三個人住但係bk二人房<br />\n<br />\n19/8 HK to Graz<br />\n20/8 到Graz 過一晚<br />\n21/8 - 23/8 salzburg 有趣去outlet<br />\n23-24/8 Hallstatt 但係酒店bk錯左 bk左Gosau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n24-25/8 CK 一日可以行晒 不過前幾日去有兩團講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該係一台灣一大陸<br />\n25-27/8 Prague 又outlet<br />\n27-29/8 Wien 咩景點都冇去 俾我阿媽逼我帶佢去outlet 之後狂買swarovski<br />\n29-31/8 原定返graz住 因為佢兩個31號機返香港<br />\n不過宜家去左同鄉屋企過一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12908f8d484af35295be0fa100e023695557dbd1","tid":375542,"uid":3980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟宜家身在奧地利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身因為exchange要過嚟 家母同細佬跟埋嚟個幾禮拜 本身hea plan路線都冇plan行程 同埋酒店都係一個禮拜前bk 所以都好貴 三個人咁多晚都過萬二 因為我唔肯屈蛇 姐係三個人住但係bk二人房<br />\n<br />\n19/8 HK to Graz<br />\n20/8 到Graz 過一晚<br />\n21/8 - 23/8 salzburg 有趣去outlet<br />\n23-24/8 Hallstatt 但係酒店bk錯左 bk左Gosau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n24-25/8 CK 一日可以行晒 不過前幾日去有兩團講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該係一台灣一大陸<br />\n25-27/8 Prague 又outlet<br />\n27-29/8 Wien 咩景點都冇去 俾我阿媽逼我帶佢去outlet 之後狂買swarovski<br />\n29-31/8 原定返graz住 因為佢兩個31號機返香港<br />\n不過宜家去左同鄉屋企過一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都幾chur 大部分時間都係搭車<br />\n三個人三個gip 將兩個放第一晚酒店 因為29會去返果到住<br />\n跟住就一人一個背囊 加一個gip 周圍去<br />\n交通都有啲麻煩 而且比較貴 尤其hallstatt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我住gosau<br />\n<br />\nprague同埋奧地利 如果情況同埋時間許可就買day ticket啦 抵啲"},{"pid":"89c270dcf630b88604a1e6a5383f037a058b48fc","tid":375542,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟宜家身在奧地利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身因為exchange要過嚟 家母同細佬跟埋嚟個幾禮拜 本身hea plan路線都冇plan行程 同埋酒店都係一個禮拜前bk 所以都好貴 三個人咁多晚都過萬二 因為我唔肯屈蛇 姐係三個人住但係bk二人房<br />\n<br />\n19/8 HK to Graz<br />\n20/8 到Graz 過一晚<br />\n21/8 - 23/8 salzburg 有趣去outlet<br />\n23-24/8 Hallstatt 但係酒店bk錯左 bk左Gosau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n24-25/8 CK 一日可以行晒 不過前幾日去有兩團講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該係一台灣一大陸<br />\n25-27/8 Prague 又outlet<br />\n27-29/8 Wien 咩景點都冇去 俾我阿媽逼我帶佢去outlet 之後狂買swarovski<br />\n29-31/8 原定返graz住 因為佢兩個31號機返香港<br />\n不過宜家去左同鄉屋企過一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\noutlet 游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9159e33e1ec1b78f744440569b1c4a47cd492b1f","tid":375542,"uid":133320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:03:47.000Z","msg":"睇你點玩 prague我留左幾日都未行晒 <br />\n去ck 搭巴士會平過火車"},{"pid":"39ddb35ad63bbc1ab6bc7eeb4a467d1d785b7afc","tid":375542,"uid":82325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:36:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完Wien 同Prague 番黎<br />\n其實Prague 都唔錯，睇下景飲下啤酒又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果Prague 去ck 就買student agency , 方便又快捷，就咁比E-ticket 佢睇就得。ck又真係半日可以玩曬（除非你去划艇 ），不過都值得一去，本人覺得果度幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果陣由Prague 去Wien 都係搭&Ouml;BB, 你試下去佢官網買啦， 買完之前記得要印張ticket 出黎，就咁show E ticket 係唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c5087f50310c7888993a7bcca6e4030c1a445b","tid":375542,"uid":82325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟宜家身在奧地利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身因為exchange要過嚟 家母同細佬跟埋嚟個幾禮拜 本身hea plan路線都冇plan行程 同埋酒店都係一個禮拜前bk 所以都好貴 三個人咁多晚都過萬二 因為我唔肯屈蛇 姐係三個人住但係bk二人房<br />\n<br />\n19/8 HK to Graz<br />\n20/8 到Graz 過一晚<br />\n21/8 - 23/8 salzburg 有趣去outlet<br />\n23-24/8 Hallstatt 但係酒店bk錯左 bk左Gosau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n24-25/8 CK 一日可以行晒 不過前幾日去有兩團講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該係一台灣一大陸<br />\n25-27/8 Prague 又outlet<br />\n27-29/8 Wien 咩景點都冇去 俾我阿媽逼我帶佢去outlet 之後狂買swarovski<br />\n29-31/8 原定返graz住 因為佢兩個31號機返香港<br />\n不過宜家去左同鄉屋企過一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\noutlet 游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全無留意到Prague 係有outlet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}